Package: kmar
Title: Korea Meteorological Administration API For R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person(given = "Chanyub", 
                  family = "Park", 
                  role = c("aut","cre"), 
                  email = "mrchypark@gmail.com", 
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6474-2570")
                  )
Description: Provides a user-friendly interface to access and retrieve data 
    from the Korea Meteorological Administration (KMA) API Hub. 
    This package simplifies API authentication, request construction, 
    and data parsing, allowing users to easily obtain real-time and 
    historical weather data, forecasts, and climate information 
    for various locations in South Korea. 
    Designed for researchers, developers, and analysts working with meteorological data.
